lead_paragraph: PHILLIPS--Elizabeth, a highly respected private dealer in rare livre d'artiste with a specialty in Russian and Eastern European avant-garde, died in New York City, December 14, 2015. She is deeply missed by her children, Julian and Hannah, and by many loving family members, friends and business associates. 1/3
